text: Kharino () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Gaynskoye Rural Settlement, Gaynsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 823 as of 2010. There are 16 streets. == Geography == It is located 6 km from Gayny. == References == Category:Rural localities in Gaynsky District
title: Kharino, Gaynsky District, Perm Krai
